{"TopicId":143610,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Does KSP refuse to minimise sometimes?","CreatedByName":"THX1138","CreatedById":113955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T12:08:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"THX1138","CreatedById":113955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T12:08:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOften during loading/changing scenes, KSP refuses to minimise when I press Alt \u002B Tab and I have to wait and look at the hung screen until it\u0027s finished at which point it lets me Alt \u002B Tab (which defeats the purpose because I wanted to Alt \u002B Tab to avoid the wait). Is it the same for everyone or specific to me?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T13:38:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022refuse\u0022 is the wrong word, \u0022is literally unable to respond to any input\u0022 is more like it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"THX1138","CreatedById":113955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T13:48:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it KSP or Windows (7 in my case) that is responsible? If I hold Alt \u002B Tab then I can see other windows (with the Alt \u002B Tab list of windows in the middle) but when I release, I got straight back to unresponsive KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T13:55:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP, because it\u0027s too busy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DChurchill","CreatedById":60282,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T14:56:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222672561\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468331733\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00222511\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Corona688\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, Corona688 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP, because it\u0027s too busy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis. It does it to me too. Patience, grasshopper. Give it a second.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eddiew","CreatedById":127483,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T14:58:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLoading screens are the worst time to alt-tab though, because that\u0027s when the hard drive is being hammered hardest and most things loaded/unloaded...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t have an SSD, look into getting one though. KSP, even modded, is much much faster from solid state than mechanical hard drive \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"THX1138","CreatedById":113955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T15:08:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222672634\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468335386\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002260282\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DChurchill\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, DChurchill said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis. It does it to me too. Patience, grasshopper. Give it a second.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou clearly have a much better computer than I do!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DChurchill","CreatedById":60282,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-12T15:09:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222672649\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468336094\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022THX1138\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, THX1138 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou clearly have a much better computer than I do!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK, 10 seconds. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}